    "description": "Get unique and amazing Dogs by either transmuting them yourself or by buying directly from the shop. Arrange your Dogs and troops to suit the battlefield needs using your wits and battle other players in a 'Tower Defense' style match!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/5c8dbbbcd627b07c98d8fe2528a8149c.avif?t=1721754381\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br>Elemental Dog Defense allows you to create your own strategy by carefully planning every detail or by transmuting everything and hoping for the best!<br><br><i>I will go the Earth/Air Dog build this time...</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/1ef98f6856dcddc23a9aef1cb62eae51.poster.avif?t=1721754381\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/1ef98f6856dcddc23a9aef1cb62eae51.webm?t=1721754381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/1ef98f6856dcddc23a9aef1cb62eae51.mp4?t=1721754381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>A plan? What's that?</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/ac021d8a038d7fa25781f2027e67e5f1.poster.avif?t=1721754381\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/ac021d8a038d7fa25781f2027e67e5f1.webm?t=1721754381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/ac021d8a038d7fa25781f2027e67e5f1.mp4?t=1721754381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/c4f7863bcb5e56fa321a716f71d9a105.avif?t=1721754381\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br>Dogs come in different shapes and forms, but every Dog originates from the basic 5 elements!<br><br><i>Fire, Water, Earth, Air and Void</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/b938beea7d3362ebcc9a52ccb404900c.avif?t=1721754381\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087110/extras/c5f0fd35bb0a1872f451daf63aa5cde3.avif?t=1721754381\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br>You are matched against real builds of other players. See how your strategy fares against your opponent and determine your true skill level! By winning, you earn MMR, which is used to match you against opponents of similar skill levels and to show who's the best on the global leaderboard in the Discord Server!<br><br>With this purchase, you will get access to play online PvP async 'Tower Defense' battles. This game is constantly evolving and receives regular updates. We maintain open communication with the community, especially on Discord.",
